  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No-nonsense brawling, arcade style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Final Vendetta delivers classic side-scrolling combat with modern polish. Inspired by the legendary beat ‘em ups of the 1990s, it challenges you to master hard-hitting combos, precise timing, and relentless momentum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The streets of London are under siege by the Syndic8 gang. When martial artist Claire Sparks’ sister is kidnapped, she joins forces with wrestler Miller T. Williams and bare-knuckle brawler Duke Sancho. Together they will fight through six urban zones to bring her home and crush anyone who stands in their way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick Your Fighter</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claire Sparks: Fast, technical, and deadly with her fists and feet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duke Sancho: A street-smart fighter with powerful punches and flashy style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Miller T. Williams: A former pro wrestler built for slams and chaos</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character brings a distinct moveset and feel. Master blocking, juggling, running attacks, and more across multiple modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Authentic Arcade Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Final Vendetta captures the look, sound, and feel of classic coin-op brawlers. It features gorgeous pixel art, responsive controls, and a thumping original soundtrack from Utah Saints, Featurecast, and Krafty Kuts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether solo or with a friend, this is pure arcade action with no filler and no mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast, fluid, and unforgiving 2D combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three playable characters with unique styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four modes: Arcade, Survival, Versus, Boss Rush</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six distinct stages packed with enemies and bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple difficulty settings and unlockables</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A pounding soundtrack featuring UK dance music legends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No-nonsense brawling, arcade style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Final Vendetta delivers classic side-scrolling combat with modern polish. Inspired by the legendary beat ‘em ups of the 1990s, it challenges you to master hard-hitting combos, precise timing, and relentless momentum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The streets of London are under siege by the Syndic8 gang. When martial artist Claire Sparks’ sister is kidnapped, she joins forces with wrestler Miller T. Williams and bare-knuckle brawler Duke Sancho. Together they will fight through six urban zones to bring her home and crush anyone who stands in their way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick Your Fighter</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claire Sparks: Fast, technical, and deadly with her fists and feet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duke Sancho: A street-smart fighter with powerful punches and flashy style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Miller T. Williams: A former pro wrestler built for slams and chaos</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character brings a distinct moveset and feel. Master blocking, juggling, running attacks, and more across multiple modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Authentic Arcade Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Final Vendetta captures the look, sound, and feel of classic coin-op brawlers. It features gorgeous pixel art, responsive controls, and a thumping original soundtrack from Utah Saints, Featurecast, and Krafty Kuts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether solo or with a friend, this is pure arcade action with no filler and no mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast, fluid, and unforgiving 2D combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three playable characters with unique styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four modes: Arcade, Survival, Versus, Boss Rush</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six distinct stages packed with enemies and bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple difficulty settings and unlockables</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A pounding soundtrack featuring UK dance music legends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
